quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  104,1,Woe unto every slandering backbiter
  104,2,who amasses wealth and tallies it
  104,3,supposing that his wealth makes him immortal
  104,4,Nay! He shall surely be cast into the crushing Fire
  104,5,And what shall apprise thee of the crushing Fire
  104,6,"The Fire of God, ignited"
  104,7,which engulfs hearts
  104,8,Truly it is enclosed upon them
  104,9,in pillars outstretched